Detailed Description

A search match for an item.

wf_uint32  distanceFromSearchPos = WF_MAX_UINT32 
)

Constructor.

Parameters:
name The name of the match.
id The identification string of the match, can be used to get more details about it.
type The type of item this match is.
subType If the SearchItem type is POI this is the type of Point Of Interest.
distance The distance this match is from the position used in the search.
locationName The names of the area(s) that the match is located in.
position The coordinate that the match is at.
imageName The name of the icon that represents this match.
advert If this match is an advertisement.
additionalInformation More details about a search item is only filled in if the SearchItem is from a searchDetails reply.
distanceFromSearchPos The distance from the position that was used when doing the search.
